:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"Author";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:5:"entry";a:17:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:103:"WordPress Francophone : L’Hebdo WordPress n°208 : WordCamp Paris 2014 – BuddyPress 1.9 – Brèves";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/eWMHFBm5mpY/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:67:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~3/eWMHFBm5mpY/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2013-11-19T07:39:25+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"anonymous";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5580:"<div>\n<h3>WordCamp Paris 2014</h3>\n<p>On sait donc que le WordCamp Paris 2014 se d&eacute;roulera les 17 et 18 janvier prochain. L&rsquo;<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://2014.paris.wordcamp.org/2013/11/13/appel-a-sponsors/">appel &agrave; sponsors est lanc&eacute;</a>. Si vous voulez nous aider dans l&rsquo;organisation de cet &eacute;v&eacute;nement alors devenez partenaire ! Si vous voulez &ecirc;tre sur sc&egrave;ne et partager votre passion pour WordPress, alors <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://2014.paris.wordcamp.org/2013/10/29/appel-a-orateurs/">l&rsquo;appel &agrave; orateur est ici</a>.</p>\n<h3>WordCamp Cape Town</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YOVqmjgdEcg&amp;feature=youtu.be">Le WordCamp du Cap se vend en vid&eacute;o</a> (en). Classe !</p>\n<h3>Un forum pour les WordCamp</h3>\n<p>WordCamp Central met en place un <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://plan.wordcamp.org/forums/">forum pour les organisateurs</a> (en).</p>\n<h3>Langage et vocabulaire</h3>\n<p>Diane fait le point sur<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://dianebourque.com/2013/11/11/le-langage-et-vocabulaire-de-wordpress/"> les langages et vocabulaires utilis&eacute;es dans WordPress</a>.</p>\n<h3>BuddyPress et le futur de son th&egrave;me par d&eacute;faut</h3>\n<p>La version 1.9 de BuddyPress va red&eacute;finir <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://bpdevel.wordpress.com/2013/11/13/the-future-of-the-bp-default-theme/">la strat&eacute;gie du th&egrave;me par d&eacute;faut </a>(en) pour <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://bp-fr.net/la-fin-du-theme-bp-default/">pr&eacute;parer son abandon</a>.</p>\n<h3>BuddyPress 1.9 Beta 1</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://buddypress.org/2013/11/buddypress-1-9-beta-1-is-now-available/">BuddyPress 1.9 beta 1 est disponible</a>. (en)</p>\n<h3>Pippin en interview</h3>\n<p>Pippin Williamson bien connu pour son site pippinsplugins.com a &eacute;t&eacute; <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://build.codepoet.com/2013/11/13/pippin-williamson-interview/">interview&eacute; par Code Poet</a>.</p>\n<h3>Am&eacute;liorer vos commentaires</h3>\n<p>Willy propose son extension qui va permettre d&rsquo;am&eacute;liorer la gestion des commentaires de votre site : <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.geekpress.fr/wordpress/extension/mention-comments-authors-1961/">Mention Comment&rsquo;s Author</a>. Cette extension permet de r&eacute;pondre aux commentaires pr&eacute;c&eacute;dents de mani&egrave;re intuitive.</p>\n<h3>Mettre &agrave; jour WordPress automatiquement ?</h3>\n<p>C&rsquo;est la question que se pose Rodrigue.<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.cree1site.com/plugin-mise-a-jour-de-plugin-automatique/"> Voici les &eacute;l&eacute;ments de r&eacute;ponses qu&rsquo;il apporte</a>.</p>\n<h3>Une vuln&eacute;rabilit&eacute; dans le framework Themify</h3>\n<p>Une vuln&eacute;rabilit&eacute; a &eacute;t&eacute; d&eacute;couverte dans le framework Themify. <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://themify.me/blog/urgent-vulnerability-found-in-themify-framework-please-read">Toutes les informations ici</a> (en).</p>\n<h3>Mystique et les mises &agrave; jour automatiques</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.lumieredelune.com/encrelune/utilisateurs-mystique-attention,2013,11">Lumi&egrave;re de Lune met en garde les utilisateurs du th&egrave;me Mystique</a> avec les mises &agrave; jour automatique.</p>\n<h3>Pressnomics, le bon, le mauvais et le g&eacute;nial</h3>\n<p>Chris Lema fait <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://chrislema.com/pressnomics-good-bad-awesome/">son r&eacute;sum&eacute; du PressNomics.</a> (en)</p>\n<h3>WordPress 3.8 : A quoi s&rsquo;attendre ?</h3>\n<p>Quels sont les <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://slocumstudio.com/2013/11/wordpress-3-8-proposals/">nouveaut&eacute;s &agrave; attendre de WordPress 3.8 ?</a></p>\n<h3>Installer une extension depuis Github</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.wptavern.com/how-to-install-wordpress-plugins-directly-from-github">C&rsquo;est ce que nous propose de d&eacute;couvrir WPTavern</a> (en).</p>\n<h3>3 extensions pour g&eacute;rer LinkedIn</h3>\n<p>Si vous voulez int&eacute;grer <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.wpjedi.com/linkedin-import-wordpress-plugins/">votre compte LinkedIn avec votre site web</a> (en), voici des extensions utiles.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=eWMHFBm5mpY:WWGPBaP3lrg:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=eWMHFBm5mpY:WWGPBaP3lrg:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=eWMHFBm5mpY:WWGPBaP3lrg:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=eWMHFBm5mpY:WWGPBaP3lrg:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=eWMHFBm5mpY:WWGPBaP3lrg:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=eWMHFBm5mpY:WWGPBaP3lrg:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></a>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/eWMHFBm5mpY" height="1" width="1">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:41:"L''écho des plugins WordPress : Post Time";s:7:"attr